      "id": "PopularPost183763",
      "post_content": "As now \"enchanted creture cannot attack\" doesn't remove already attacked creature from an attack. At least [Pacifism](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pacifism) played as an instant during an attack doesn't do it.  \n  \nWoTC is figuring out should it or shouldn't it remove the attacker and you can expect rulings coming out.",
